version_description:
We update the Shasha app as often as possible to make it faster and more reliable for you. Here are a couple of the enhancements you'll find in the latest update:

- Fix bugs when create new reservation of a seat.

- Updates all dependencies to take advantage of new swift 5 .

- Make the app more computable with iPhone X Family.

- Update app style.

if you have any questions connect us using the app support .
